REPLACEMENT PART NUMBERS: WPW10526114 Dishwasher Access Panel, Black replaces the part numbers W10368715, W10368719, W10369029, W10579090, and W10526114

body.description: This Dishwasher Access Panel, Black, covers and shields the wiring and components at the bottom front of the dishwasher. If your current panel is cracked or broken, replacing this part may alleviate the issue. This high-quality and durable dishwasher access panel is easy to install and will only require basic hand tools, such as a multi-screwdriver. No disassembly of the dishwasher or repair experience is required. Make sure you unplug the dishwasher or shut off the house circuit breaker for the appliance before installing this replacement part. Helpful Tip: We also recommend using affresh® Dishwasher Cleaner (item W10282479) to help remove limescale and mineral build-up that can be unsightly and affect your dishwasher’s performance. *affresh® brand products are owned and distributed by Whirlpool Corporation.
